{"tid":204000,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔好搵返佢?","createTime":"2017-04-16T16:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T06:28:03.000Z","uid":91618,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"872b8bfc2c6921955b15619b00d1a5a9cfd53a4e","tid":204000,"uid":91618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:53:31.000Z","msg":"識咗個男仔一年 3個月後一齊咗<br />\n後來我投訴佢忙 佢就建議返去之前咁當仲追緊我<br />\n之後都keep住日日聯絡啦 <br />\n但慢慢我覺得佢係拖住我 好幾次我話想一齊返佢都唔肯<br />\n佢話怕太忙我又會唔開心 加上我又即將離開香港一年<br />\n其實我明 但真係好介意佢一路都冇心同我一齊 永遠要我等<br />\n上上星期終於狠心del哂佢電話同所有訊息 仲喊咗好幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢有搵我想傾 話返黎後先再諗一唔一齊 <br />\n但我真係好想佢呢家就答應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇理佢幾日 我真係好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59f1924c7bc5b54d71143bee78fc214366f5d1c","tid":204000,"uid":74962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:55:59.000Z","msg":"條女很清楚&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n好心唔好咁婆媽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8196c291f7022a01a09479bf81a39d8ae3e15bea","tid":204000,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"忙都要投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4144854585d0e9186b62b2dc50f5d7835671ce60","tid":204000,"uid":86476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"唔好啦"},{"pid":"d4a31cc67a0ed737b0a192cce5cf4f48a4120ac2","tid":204000,"uid":91618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條女很清楚&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n好心唔好咁婆媽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家係條仔<br />\n鬧我啦 大力啲唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5c5ca446c8dfd00f399ad63ad1b1bb7362952f","tid":204000,"uid":91618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":